## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the rapidly changing nature of the COVID-19 pandemic. The information is based on sources available up to October 2023, and newer developments may not be reflected. Additionally, the focus is primarily on the U.S. healthcare system, and findings may not be applicable to other countries with different healthcare infrastructures.